00:47:55,047 --> 00:47:56,648
it's clear that somebody has done...

825
00:47:57,250 --> 00:47:58,631
zero investigation.

826
00:47:58,631 --> 00:48:01,814
So I've had candidates, especially abroad,

827
00:48:01,814 --> 00:48:06,838
that did zero investigation into local cost of living.

828
00:48:06,838 --> 00:48:09,420
And literally were asking for more money

829
00:48:09,420 --> 00:48:11,462
than directors at the company made.

830
00:48:11,462 --> 00:48:14,104
You know, it's a really hard place to start.

