00:50:24,866 --> 00:50:29,588
What kind of resources can you recommend for that sort of very niche?

869
00:50:30,218 --> 00:50:31,699
It's all about networking.

870
00:50:31,699 --> 00:50:34,561
You got to know the people in your industry and you got to be

