00:50:46,488 --> 00:50:48,429
is that it's a salary that's much higher than yours, right?

877
00:50:48,429 --> 00:50:50,410
So that opens you up to a lot of vulnerability.

878
00:50:50,410 --> 00:50:52,212
But I think that is the way forward, especially in those

879
00:50:52,212 --> 00:50:53,152
niche industries.

880
00:50:53,152 --> 00:50:56,154
It's like you need that you can get this information from peers

881
00:50:56,154 --> 00:50:57,375
around you too.

882
00:50:57,929 --> 00:51:01,431
And one of the great things specifically for narrative,

883
00:51:01,431 --> 00:51:06,673
it's sort of like art this way, is that you have an incredibly unique portfolio.

884
00:51:06,673 --> 00:51:15,177
You have something that nobody else has that's applying for that job, which is your body of work.

885
00:51:15,177 --> 00:51:18,819
So it's especially with 13 years in the career, in your career,

886
00:51:18,819 --> 00:51:22,400
you should go into that being like, you know who I am.

