00:52:08,195 --> 00:52:12,718
I think you kind of answered it for yourself a little bit there is getting those mentors,

897
00:52:12,718 --> 00:52:18,163
finding, you know, one or two individuals who are doing the thing that you want to do

898
00:52:18,163 --> 00:52:24,088
that will help coach you, you know, and mentorship is not this strict program where you, you know,

899
00:52:24,088 --> 00:52:27,631
have to have this meeting and then this meeting, this meeting, then it's done.

900
00:52:27,631 --> 00:52:31,674
A mentorship is like any other relationship. They may not have all of the answers,

