00:53:01,610 --> 00:53:03,311
And I met my mentor on Twitter.

910
00:53:04,486 --> 00:53:07,788
really a mentor when you boil everything else down,

911
00:53:07,788 --> 00:53:09,889
is somebody who's interested in what you have to offer

912
00:53:09,889 --> 00:53:10,950
and who believes in you.

913
00:53:10,950 --> 00:53:13,552
So strike up conversations with people

914
00:53:13,552 --> 00:53:15,753
who are sort of in that sweet spot,

